</item>
<item>
<title><code>value</code></title>
  <p>A pointer to a 2 component float vector</p>
</item>
<item>
<title><code>Returns</code></title>
  <p>A newly allocated <link xref="Cogl.Attribute"/>
         representing the given constant vector.</p>
